rap below the right aligned image and settle in nicely. There should still be plenty of room and everything should be sitting pretty. Yeah... Just like that. It never felt so good to be right.\n\nAnd that\'s a wrap, yo! You survived the tumultuous waters of alignment. Image alignment achievement unlocked!', 'Image Alignment', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'image-alignment', '', '', '2013-01-10 20:15:40', '2013-01-11 02:15:40', '', 0, 'http://wptest.io/demo/?p=903', 0, 'post', '', 0),
